==English==

===Noun===
'''adaptability'''
# The quality of being [[adaptable]]; a quality that renders adaptable.
# {{biology}} Variability in respect to, or under the influence of, [[external]] [[condition]]s; [[susceptibility]] of an organism to that variation whereby it becomes suited to or fitted for its conditions of environment; the capacity of an organism to be [[modify|modified]] by circumstances.

